flowchart TD
    START[User Enters] --> OC{Overconfidence Check}
    
    OC -->|Claims expertise| TEST[Test: Explain in own words]
    OC -->|No claims| DETECT{Can engage with topic?}
    
    TEST --> RESULT{Result?}
    RESULT -->|Deep| DIRECT
    RESULT -->|Shallow| FOUNDATION
    RESULT -->|Zero| FOUNDATION
    
    DETECT -->|Yes, has experience| DIRECT[Direct Protocol]
    DETECT -->|No, zero background| FOUNDATION[Foundation Mode]
    
    DIRECT --> D1[Step 1: Intent + Context]
    D1 --> D2[Step 2: Concrete Situation]
    D2 --> D3[Step 3: Articulation Through Application]
    D3 --> D4[Step 4: Reflective Challenge]
    D4 --> CHECK{Shallow or Deep?}
    CHECK -->|Shallow| D4
    CHECK -->|Deep| D5[Step 5: Reflection Log]
    D5 --> COMPLETE[Topic Complete]
    
    FOUNDATION --> F1[F1: Acknowledge Starting Point]
    F1 --> F2[F2: Grounding Context]
    F2 --> F3[F3: Immediate Verification]
    F3 --> FCHECK{Verified?}
    FCHECK -->|No| F2
    FCHECK -->|Yes| F4[F4: Application Challenge]
    F4 --> F5[F5: Transition]
    F5 --> DIRECT
    
    COMPLETE --> SESSION{Session Status}
    SESSION -->|Continue| NEXT[Next Topic]
    SESSION -->|End| WRAP[Session Wrap-up]
    
    NEXT --> DETECT
    
    NORTH[Core: Verify understanding through demonstration] -.-> START
